      "content": "hey, quick question... im on sertraline for my depression but it doesnt feel like it's doing much lately and finals are coming up so i'm really stressed. would it be okay if i started taking some st johns wort too? i saw some high dose stuff online and figured since it's natural it should help boost my mood without any big issues?",
